    },
    {
      "id": "d3-ann2-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 955,
      "y": 335,
      "width": 275.36566162109375,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd65z6mbkxr0tkqu6u"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b00",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1829023112,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1152223624,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772701378025,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The symlink problem\n\nProblem: Skills are installed as symlinks,\nbut Node.js says symlinks aren't folders.\nA naive scan would miss every skill.\n\nSolution: A helper checks \"is this a\nsymlink?\" first, then follows it to see if\nthe target is a real folder. Two-step\ncheck that works on all platforms.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The symlink problem\n\nProblem: Skills are installed as symlinks,\nbut Node.js says symlinks aren't folders.\nA naive scan would miss every skill.\n\nSolution: A helper checks \"is this a\nsymlink?\" first, then follows it to see if\nthe target is a real folder. Two-step\ncheck that works on all platforms.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "syncedAt": "2026-03-05T09:16:04.024Z",
      "source": "frontend_sync",
      "syncTimestamp": "2026-03-05T09:16:03.713Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d3-ann3-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
