    {
      "id": "d3-ann3-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 955,
      "y": 545,
      "width": 264.4176330566406,
      "height": 157.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd65zj2582agirmazp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b02",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1780857992,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 273881224,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772701378025,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Why deduplicate?\n\nProblem: The same skill is symlinked\ninto 5+ agent folders. Without dedup,\nthe UI would show 5 copies.\n\nSolution: Group by folder name. Show\nthe skill once with badges listing which\nagents have it (e.g. \"Claude, Cursor\").",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Why deduplicate?\n\nProblem: The same skill is symlinked\ninto 5+ agent folders. Without dedup,\nthe UI would show 5 copies.\n\nSolution: Group by folder name. Show\nthe skill once with badges listing which\nagents have it (e.g. \"Claude, Cursor\").",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "syncedAt": "2026-03-05T09:16:04.024Z",
      "source": "frontend_sync",
      "syncTimestamp": "2026-03-05T09:16:03.713Z"
